# System-level requirements
artifact SRS:
    id is string as SCHED-{atype}-{num:3}
    attribute contents is mandatory string
    attribute parent is mandatory multiple reference to parent if not derive
    attribute func is optional string
    attribute safety is mandatory boolean [true: "yes", false: "no"]
    attribute derive is optional boolean [true: "yes", false: "no"]
    attribute alloc is optional string
    attribute doors-id is optional string
    attribute comment is optional multiple string
    attribute ratio is optional multiple string

